  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Select Elements</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Select Elements</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">If, when you select elements to do a command, there is ambiguity as to which <text styleclass="Element">Element(s)</text> to actually use for the command, the <text styleclass="Interface2">Select Elements dialog</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> </text>opens <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">automatically</text>.  </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">It lists all of the elements that you select, including the </text><text styleclass="Element">Points</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> you want to select.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You must <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">CTRL+Click</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> the elements to do the command.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Select-Elements dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-SELECT-ELEMENTS.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">In the <text styleclass="Interface2">Select-Elements dialog:</text> </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><image src="MD-Ctrlb.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;"> </text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold;">+</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;"> </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">Click </text><text styleclass="Interface2" style="font-size:16pt; color:#ff0000;">ALL</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> of the elements you need to do the command.</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> </text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">The <image src="OK-tiny-15-18.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> becomes colorized only after you select the elements that are compatible with the active command.</para>
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;">Click</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;"> </text><image src="OK-tiny-15-18.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text"> to close the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Select-Elements dialog</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">If the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Command-Manager" styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</link> is also active:</para>
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Continue to select the elements, as required. </li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">and / or</para>
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:'Segoe UI Semibold'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Click <image src="OK-tiny-15-18.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> in the <text styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</text> to complete the command.</li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
